SPARKIN away in good order, alternated up front closest to the inside, first to blink upper stretch, continued to give way. EIGHT STRAIGHT in mid pack while racing outside, had little for the drive. DOUBLE STRIKE broke back and failed to menace. PERFECT THUNDER off a step slow, raced well back throughout.
